title: HydraDeck - Humans (Hydra Scans)
description:
This is a demo where you look at some models rendered using the Laser Scan technology.
It's super realistic like nothing you've ever seen before in games. 

You can chose between 10 different lighting and you can rotate the models and the scenario.
It supports VR hardwares like Oculus Rift.

Controls:
Tab - Disable the VR view (Switch back to a normal view, without the split screen)
Left Mouse while looking at a model: Makes it rotate.
Mouse Wheel UP and DOWN = Rotate the scenario
Numbers 1 - 0: Changes the lighting
